{"id": 801, "genre": 1001, "title": "你受不了哪种网剧？", "description": "人人都在烧IP，但网剧真的好看吗？（题图来自：Janne Livonen）", "record_count": 5586, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183518kpZrIBPvb6UWXnMG.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-02-05T11:28:47Z", "options": [{"id": 135436, "content": "面瘫脸，人设玛丽苏，爱情占大头，剧情狗血", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 826621}, {"id": 48909, "content": "我觉得很不错啊，生活中很好的调味剂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 465613}, {"id": 47120, "content": "名字山寨", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 458688}, {"id": 49938, "content": "剧情低俗矫情古装片演员妆容妖死的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469401}, {"id": 48152, "content": "尴尬的不要不要的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462271}, {"id": 49688, "content": "剧组上下对观众极布负责，很明显的那种_(:з」∠)_ 一本正经的胡说八道", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 411686}, {"id": 50972, "content": "婆媳大战、豪门恩怨、男一男二男三男四都爱我......", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 454454}, {"id": 50973, "content": "婆媳大战、豪门恩怨、男一男二男三男四都爱我......", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 454454}, {"id": 60701, "content": "啥也get不到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 528763}, {"id": 54046, "content": "不喜欢网剧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 492651}, {"id": 47137, "content": "拿脑残当喜剧的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 448375}, {"id": 49697, "content": "被我猜到剧情也就算了，被我猜到你下一秒要做什么，哭要哭多久，不用想，全中", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 464039}, {"id": 47405, "content": "面瘫脸、俗烂剧情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 390378}, {"id": 51503, "content": "青春偶像狗血剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 480352}, {"id": 46902, "content": "剧情毁三观，女主网红脸，演员演技渣", "image": null, "praise_count": 1000, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456710}, {"id": 46903, "content": "所有国产网剧，不谢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 184, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 220980}, {"id": 46904, "content": "玛丽苏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 371, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209295}, {"id": 46905, "content": "拉低智商的", "image": null, "praise_count": 527, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143798}, {"id": 46906, "content": "虽然不好看，但我们尽最大的努力了！你知道我们加班多辛苦吗？知道我们剧组多穷吗？————这样产生的网剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 134, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140661}, {"id": 46907, "content": " 狗血剧情", "image": null, "praise_count": 159, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 454484}, {"id": 47163, "content": "我用一张无奈的脸，看着他们配合假声自己笑……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142448}, {"id": 46908, "content": "穿插好多网上陈年老段子的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 398, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254572}, {"id": 49468, "content": "演员长得丑，演技还TM的烂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 467396}, {"id": 53052, "content": "看起来就想在演奥特曼的，脑残片。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487322}, {"id": 46910, "content": "跳票的网剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 60415}, {"id": 47166, "content": "结束1", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 459146}, {"id": 48702, "content": "「芈月传」。如果不是请了孙俪，他也是网剧的一种", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 463858}, {"id": 46912, "content": "一群演技奇烂无比的网红脸  凑出一部毁三观的烂剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 338, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253533}, {"id": 51009, "content": "看不下去的，蹩脚的，演员假的，不知道怎么拍出来的，怎么忍受的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471932}, {"id": 46914, "content": "没逻辑", "image": null, "praise_count": 119, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 393412}, {"id": 47170, "content": "玛丽苏 汤姆苏 狗血段子什么鬼", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 437273}, {"id": 46915, "content": "全部……", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 435399}, {"id": 48195, "content": "把观众当弱智的一切脑残剧！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462408}, {"id": 46917, "content": "太子妃升职记", "image": null, "praise_count": 260, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 280668}, {"id": 48455, "content": "男主女主比配角还丑，各种污，各种狗血，各种烂尾", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 463276}, {"id": 47177, "content": "一半笑点靠网上的过时段子，一半靠屎尿屁。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 443026}, {"id": 46922, "content": "网剧？有这种东西？好吃吗⋯⋯", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78175}, {"id": 46923, "content": "本身并不成熟，现在还被有关部门阉割", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 404441}, {"id": 49227, "content": "极尽所能迎合大众的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224612}, {"id": 46925, "content": "只要是不喜欢的人演的", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323525}, {"id": 46926, "content": "比如改编一些小说的网络剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 390149}, {"id": 46927, "content": "非主流比如明若曉溪", "image": null, "praise_count": 126, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449999}, {"id": 50000, "content": "不认识的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469870}, {"id": 46929, "content": "穿插各种植入广告的", "image": null, "praise_count": 110, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450075}, {"id": 49489, "content": "噱头一堆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161938}, {"id": 46932, "content": "奇怪的配音。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 